It appears that SyncView$SyncModeAction is being run before the 
SyncCompareInput (type of variable input) has had it's viewer initialized (by 
invokation of SyncCompareInput #createDiffViewer() which is part of the compare 
framework). This appears at first glance to be a timing issue.
